peopleAlsoAsk.question: Will Coca-Cola give you a vending machine?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: If you are interested in purchasing a soda machine that is owned by the Coca-Cola Company, you will need to reach out to their authorized distributors or vending partners. Coca-Cola does not typically sell machines directly to individuals or businesses.

peopleAlsoAsk.question: How to get a Pepsi vending machine?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: To get a vending machine, your location must meet the qualifications below: For a soda machine: Office/manufacturing - at least 40 full-time employees. Retail – 60+ employees for break room placement; 100+ if machine is accessible to the public.

peopleAlsoAsk.question: Why is Dr Pepper in Pepsi machines?
